Interface DynamicMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Message, Metadata, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Window

    public interface DynamicMetadata
extends Metadata
    Metadata tag to indicate that the information carried by this Metadata may change throughout the lifetime of the Channel and should not carry the same Persistence policies as regular metadata.
